OL,3,CCourtroom broadcasting moves step
OL,4,Ccloser as pilot begins
OL,6,FThe filming of court judgments is to
OL,7,Fbe trialed in Northern Ireland.
OL,9,FJudgments by the Court of Appeal will
OL,10,Fbe filmed but not broadcast during the
OL,11,Fpilot scheme which starts on Friday.
OL,13,FBroadcasting from courts is prohibited
OL,14,Fin Northern Ireland. The trail will
OL,15,Fgive the judiciary and broadcasters an
OL,16,Funderstanding of the technical
OL,17,Fchallenges and feasibility of filming
OL,18,Fproceedings should the ban be lifted.
