OL,6,FFilming will be carried out by
OL,7,Fbroadcasters - including UTV - who
OL,8,Fhave experience of filming proceedings
OL,9,Fin the Court of Appeal and crown
OL,10,Fcourts in England and Wales.
OL,12,FThe Lady Chief Justice of Northern
OL,13,FIreland, Dame Siobhan Keegan, is in
OL,14,Ffavour of legislation being passed
OL,15,Fwhich will allow for broadcasting in
OL,16,Fcourts in Northern Ireland ` placing
OL,17,Fthe jurisdiction on a similar footing
OL,18,Fas England, Wales and Scotland.
OL,20,F"The principle of open justice is of
OL,21,Ffundamental importance," she said.
