OL,6,F"I have long thought that the
OL,7,Fbroadcasting of our senior courts
OL,8,Fwould represent a very positive step
OL,9,Fin promoting open justice, allowing
OL,10,Fgreater transparency and helping the
OL,11,Fpublic to better understand the
OL,12,Fcomplex decisions that judges make."
OL,14,FA broadcasting spokesperson described
OL,15,Fthe pilot as a "very positive
OL,16,Fdevelopment in terms of the reporting
OL,17,Fof courts in Northern Ireland".
