OL,6,F"More transparency and openness around
OL,7,Fthe justice system can only be a good
OL,8,Fthing for all our audiences and will
OL,9,Fhelp their understanding of this
OL,10,Fimportant function in society," they
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FSolicitor Paul Dougan welcomed the
OL,14,Fnews as a positive baby step.
OL,16,FJustice Minister Naomi Long also said
OL,17,Fthe pilot scheme is "an important step
OL,18,Fforward in opening up our courts and
OL,19,Fengendering a better understanding of
OL,20,Fthe legal system here".
