OL,6,F"I look forward to continuing to
OL,7,Fengage... on this pilot scheme, which
OL,8,Fwill help inform further discussion on
OL,9,Ffuture possibilities," she said.
OL,11,F"Broadcasting in courts can already
OL,12,Fhappen in England, Scotland and Wales
OL,13,Fin certain circumstances. Any future
OL,14,Fdecision to introduce this in Northern
OL,15,FIreland would require legislative
OL,16,Fchanges to enable it to become
OL,17,Fembedded in the court process."
