OL,6,FMs Long added: "I look forward to
OL,7,Fseeing the evaluation of the pilot
OL,8,Fscheme and am open to a discussion on
OL,9,Fany recommendations that might be
OL,10,Fbrought forward.
OL,12,F"Allowing broadcasting in courts would
OL,13,Fincrease transparency and enable the
OL,14,Fpublic to view decisions being made by
OL,15,Fthe judiciary in Northern Ireland.
OL,16,FThis can only be a good thing."
